dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of 12 million clicked (question-form query, standard query) pairs, used for training the DeepProbe model to generate standard queries from question-form queries.

dcterms:description: A fully annotated test set containing (query, ad) pairs labeled by human judges according to the relevance between the query and the ad, used for evaluating the DeepProbe scoring model.
